record.title: AUTHORIZING THE CLERK TO MAKE CORRECTIONS IN ENGROSSMENT OF H.R. 2764, THE DEPARTMENT OF STATE, FOREIGN OPERATIONS AND RELATED PROGRAMS APPROPRIATIONS ACT, 2008; AND H.R. 2771, LEGISLATIVE BRANCH APPROPRIATIONS ACT, 2008

speaking-unknown-id.title: Ms.
speaking-unknown-id.name: SCHULTZ, WASSERMAN
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Madam Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that the Clerk be authorized to make technical corrections in the engrossment of H.R. 2764 and H.R. 2771, to include corrections in spelling, punctuation, section number and cross-referencing, and the insertion of appropriate headings.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentlewoman from Florida?
